TITLE: Foreign volunteers race to train new Ukrainian troops to be sent to the front
SUMMARY: Magnus Ek, 53, a retired Swedish lieutenant, is teaching a group of Ukrainian conscripts how to fire an AK-47 in eastern Ukraine's Donbas region.
